2026-07-09 20:45:23 India Standard Time | INFO     | NeuroSan:_log:720 - NeuroSan - {"message": "The resulting agent network content: { # Importing content from other HOCON files # The include keyword must be unquoted and followed by a quoted URL or file path. # File paths should be absolute or relative to the script's working directory, not the HOCON file location. # This "aaosa.hocon" file contains key-value pairs used for substitution. # Specifically, it provides values for the following keys: #   - aaosa_call #   - aaosa_instructions # IMPORTANT: # Ensure that you run `python -m neuro_san_studio run` from the top level of the repository. # The path to this substitution file is **relative to the top-level directory**, # so running the script from elsewhere may result in file not found errors. include "registries/aaosa.hocon" # Optional metadata describing this agent network "metadata": { "sample_queries": [ """A fire at our primary warehouse in Germany has halted all shipping. Please provide an executive summary on the operational, financial, and legal impact, along with a draft press release.""", """We are facing a sudden supply chain disruption in Southeast Asia due to local port strikes. Assess the impact on our Q4 inventory and provide a risk mitigation plan.""", """A potential data breach has been reported in our customer database. Please analyze our immediate legal exposure and draft an internal memo for employees.""" ], "date_created": "2026-07-09T15:15:23.063182+00:00" }, # Load the shared LLM configuration from a single source of truth. # This allows users to change the model in one file rather than # modifying the configuration for each agent network. # Note that the file path here is relative to the root level of the repo. include "config/llm_config.hocon", "instructions_prefix": """ You are part of a team of assistants in sentinel_crisis_command. Only answer inquiries that are directly within your area of expertise. Do not try to help for other matters. Do not mention what you can NOT do. Only mention what you can do. """, "demo_mode": "You are part of a demo system, so when queried, make up a realistic response as if you are actually grounded in real data or you are operating a real application API or microservice.", "tools": [ { "name": "Chief_of_Staff", "function": ${aaosa_call}{ "description": """ Acts as the central orchestrator for crisis management, delegating tasks to specialized agents and synthesizing their findings into executive summaries for leadership. """ }, "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """ Never express irrelevance unless you have first consulted all your tools. Once you have determined the relevant tools, do not express that to the user, rather, call all the relevant tools and make sure the command is fully serviced and express the end result. You are the central orchestrator. When a crisis is reported, analyze the situation and delegate specific tasks to the SAP_SupplyChain_Agent, Finance_Risk_Agent, Legal_Agent, and PR_Comms_Agent. Once you receive their reports, synthesize their findings into a concise, actionable executive summary for the CEO. """ ${aaosa_instructions}, "tools": ["SAP_SupplyChain_Agent", "Finance_Risk_Agent", "Legal_Agent", "PR_Comms_Agent"] }, { "name": "SAP_SupplyChain_Agent", "function": ${aaosa_call}{ "description": """ Assesses the impact of crises on global logistics, inventory, supply lines, and production schedules, while proposing mitigation strategies. """ }, "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} ${demo_mode} """ You are an expert in global logistics and SAP systems. Your role is to assess the impact of the crisis on current inventory, supply lines, and production schedules. Identify immediate bottlenecks and propose viable workarounds or alternative sourcing strategies. """, }, { "name": "Finance_Risk_Agent", "function": ${aaosa_call}{ "description": """ Quantifies financial impact, including revenue loss, operational costs, and insurance coverage, providing projections during crises. """ }, "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} ${demo_mode} """ You are a financial risk analyst. Your role is to quantify the financial impact of the crisis, including estimated revenue loss, potential operational costs, and an assessment of applicable insurance coverage. Provide clear financial projections based on the crisis data. """, }, { "name": "Legal_Agent", "function": ${aaosa_call}{ "description": """ Provides legal analysis of crisis situations, focusing on liability, contractual obligations, and regulatory compliance. """ }, "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} ${demo_mode} """ You are a corporate legal counsel. Your role is to evaluate the crisis through the lens of liability. Identify contractual obligations, potential breaches, regulatory risks, and necessary legal precautions to mitigate exposure. """, }, { "name": "PR_Comms_Agent", "function": ${aaosa_call}{ "description": """ Drafts and manages strategic internal and external communications to maintain corporate reputation during a crisis. """ }, "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} ${demo_mode} """ You are a communications specialist. Your role is to draft clear, empathetic, and strategic messaging for both internal (employees) and external (stakeholders, public) audiences. Ensure that all communications align with corporate values and mitigate reputational damage. """, }, ] } ", "user_id": "None", "Timestamp": "2026-07-09T20:45:23.063286", "source": "HttpServer", "message_type": "Other", "request_id": "request-18"}
