2026-07-09 20:45:23 India Standard Time | INFO     | NeuroSan:_log:720 - NeuroSan:HttpServer: Done with agent_network_designer.StreamingChat request for 'Build a multi-agent network called 'Sentinel Crisis Command'. The network should have one front-man agent called 'Chief_of_Staff' who receives a description of a corporate crisis from the user. The Chief_of_Staff must delegate tasks to four specialized agents: 1. 'SAP_SupplyChain_Agent' which analyzes inventory impacts and finds workarounds. 2. 'Finance_Risk_Agent' which calculates revenue loss and insurance coverage. 3. 'Legal_Agent' which checks contract liabilities. 4. 'PR_Comms_Agent' which drafts internal and external communications. The Chief_of_Staff should compile their answers into a final executive summary. Create the full HOCON configuration with detailed instructions for each agent's persona and responsibilities.'
2026-07-09 20:45:23 India Standard Time | INFO     | nsflow:_log:720 - nsflow: {"type": "AI", "text": "The 'Sentinel Crisis Command' agent network has been successfully created.\n\n### Network Structure\n- **Chief_of_Staff**: Central orchestrator that delegates tasks and synthesizes findings into an executive summary.\n- **SAP_SupplyChain_Agent**: Analyzes inventory impacts, production schedules, and proposes logistics workarounds.\n- **Finance_Risk_Agent**: Quantifies revenue loss, operational costs, and assesses insurance coverage.\n- **Legal_Agent**: Evaluates contractual liabilities, regulatory risks, and mitigation strategies.\n- **PR_Comms_Agent**: Drafts strategic internal and external communications to maintain reputation.\n\n### Sample Queries\n1. \"A major supplier in Southeast Asia has declared force majeure due to a regional flood. Assess the impact on our Q3 production and draft a communication strategy.\"\n2. \"We have detected a significant data breach involving customer personal information. Analyze the potential legal liability, financial exposure, and draft an internal memo to all employees.\"\n3. \"A critical failure in our primary distribution warehouse has halted all outgoing shipments for the last 48 hours. What is the estimated revenue loss, and what are our immediate supply chain workarounds?\""}
